			<div id="post-988" class="hentry p2 post publish author-c4chaos category-geopolitics y2008 m07 d11 h07 alt">
				<h3 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.c4chaos.com/2008/07/ted-koppel-and-charlie-rose-on-the-peoples-republic-of-capitalism/" title="Permalink to Ted Koppel and Charlie Rose On the People&#8217;s Republic of Capitalism" rel="bookmark">Ted Koppel and Charlie Rose On the People&#8217;s Republic of Capitalism</a></h3>
				<div class="entry-date"><abbr class="published" title="2008-07-11T14:59:09+0000">Friday, July 11th, 2008</abbr></div>
				<div class="entry-content">
<p>Ted Koppel interview with Charlie Rose is now up. Sweet. Check it. Last night I watched the second installment of The People&#8217;s Republic of Capitalism &#8211; Ted Koppel&#8217;s documentary on how capitalism and globalization is changing the economic and cultural landscape of the People&#8217;s Republic of China. Part 2 was all about the cultural changes [&hellip;]</p>
