			<div id="post-861" class="hentry p3 post publish author-c4chaos category-geopolitics y2008 m05 d16 h06">
				<h3 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.c4chaos.com/2008/05/the-second-world-matters-in-a-post-american-world/" title="Permalink to The Second World Matters in a Post-American World" rel="bookmark">The Second World Matters in a Post-American World</a></h3>
				<div class="entry-date"><abbr class="published" title="2008-05-16T13:30:09+0000">Friday, May 16th, 2008</abbr></div>
				<div class="entry-content">
<p>I&#8217;ve been watching a lot of Charlie Rose conversations lately. Last night Parag Khanna was on the program discussing his views in his book, The Second World &#8211; Empires &amp; Influence in the New Global Order. Very informative and insightful discussions on geopolitics and global economics. Check it. In general, Khanna&#8217;s view is a complement [&hellip;]</p>
